Introduction

GIRLKIND was a girl group comprising five members: Medic Jin, JK, Xeheun, Sun J, and Ellyn. They had their debut on January 17, 2018, under Next Level Entertainment with the track "FANCI."

On August 13, 2022, Next Level Entertainment revealed that GIRLKIND would be disbanding because of internal challenges that hindered their continued activities.
